{"tid":2249791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實利記對愛狗成場波秀才遇著兵有理說不清","createTime":"2020-10-19T14:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T07:58:42.000Z","uid":13106,"like":26,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"23f8bda73756b66130ac742c00ad8f03ae7ca605","tid":2249791,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"愛華頓靠屈高波追和<br />\n之後即刻9縮後場死守<br />\n禁區下下6,7個人點射中龍<br />\n再加埋精湛演技呃下牌拖下時間<br />\n<br />\n高普為人太正氣<br />\n對住呢d三流既爛仔軍團<br />\n明刀明槍真係蝕曬章<br />\n<br />\n望留而家成隊利<br />\n冇錯個個都好正氣好好波<br />\n冇乜人做小動作/碌地/撩事鬥非/噴口水等等<br />\n咪比d爛仔恰<br />\n文尼幾乎抵唔住頸拎紅牌<br />\n<br />\n但你睇下曼城<br />\n成隊演藝學院畢業<br />\n再睇下熱刺<br />\n成隊銅皮鐵骨橫衝直撞唔怕拎紅牌<br />\n佢地先治得到愛華頓"},{"pid":"eeee9f52e6d8b70d395eefac5604e8d8b6ff83c1","tid":2249791,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4298d1d61314179b733fdd53c0a177b810eed51","tid":2249791,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"收爺啦 日撚日喺度利記愛記"},{"pid":"9a0cce12dd002a6f58a6285eb286fc6fc991b006","tid":2249791,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4298d1d61314179b733fdd53c0a177b810eed51","tid":2249791,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"收爺啦 日撚日喺度利記愛記"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"樓主反猁反咗幾十年 我會選擇信佢"},{"pid":"f1bf365ee39a2b096128a65466510827d5a188e1","tid":2249791,"uid":13106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a0cce12dd002a6f58a6285eb286fc6fc991b006","tid":2249791,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4298d1d61314179b733fdd53c0a177b810eed51","tid":2249791,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T14:38:11.000Z","ms